overview:
Force-IT LLC was founded in Dubai, United Arab Emirates, in 2012 by highly experienced technical experts with fortune 500 backgrounds.

Force-IT provides solutions for the Complete Networking & Server Deployments, maintenance, configurations, structured cabling, Telephone (PABX), Access Control and Security Cameras (CCTV) and Data Center Infrastructure Like Racks/ Enclosure and UPS.

Force-IT Setup/Infrastructure includes:

• Full IT Infrastructure solutions from the scratch to fully operational. • Router/Switches/Firewall deployment and configuration • Data Center Migration • Server/Storage Deployment • Cisco IP Telephony/VOIP Solution • Wireless Solutions • Uninterruptible Power Supply (UPS) Solution • Data Center Racks/ Enclosure • Structured Cabling for Data, Voice and Surveillance • Surveillance solutions • PABX Solutions
